picom: compositor
nitrogen: wallpapers
xinput: touchscreen gestures
rofi: app launcher
kitty: terminal emulator
thunar: file manager
spectacle, scrot: screenshots
dunst: some notifications
playerctl : required for the music widget
lxappearance: for theme switching
light: brightness control
alsa-utils: volume control
fonts: Jetbrainsmono nerd font, CaskaydiaCove Nerd Font, Inter font
acpi: for battery widget
